<p><strong>Data</strong><br />
<button class="my_button_small" onclick="window.open('.', '_blank');">Data</button>
Nassif and Wilson (1975), “The influence of slope and rain intensity on runoff and infiltration”, <a href="https://yairmau.com/archive/hydrology/nassif-1975-THE-INFLUENCE-OF-SLOPE-AND-RAIN-INTENSITY-ON-RUNOFF-AND-INFILTRATION.pdf">download here</a>, figure 8 (2nd panel) from this paper <a href="https://yairmau.com/archive/hydrology/nassif-16percent-slope.png">download here</a>, 4 csv files of infiltration rate against time, <a href="https://yairmau.com/archive/hydrology/infiltration-rate.zip">download here</a>.</p>

